# OpenTofu / Terraform (INFRA-4 IaC — infra/aws/)
# Never commit local provider caches, state, plans, or real tfvars. The later
# authorized `.terraform.lock.hcl` MUST be committed, so it is NOT ignored here.
# Crash logs (crash.log / crash.*.log) are already covered by the global *.log.
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
# A real partial-backend config carries the state bucket/table/KMS identifiers
# (never committed, aws-staging-iac-plan.md §7); only the example is tracked.
backend.hcl
!backend.hcl.example
# Re-include the IaC `storage` module dir; the app-level `storage/` rule above
# (local object storage) would otherwise ignore this documentation-only stub.
!infra/aws/modules/storage/
